# 断言系统完整测试
# 测试所有类型的断言功能

### 测试 1: 状态码断言
@name Basic Status Check
@assert status == 200
GET https://httpbin.org/status/200

###

### 测试 2: 多个断言
@name Multiple Assertions Test
@assert status == 200
@assert headers.content-type contains "json"
@assert body.slideshow exists
@assert response.time < 5000
GET https://httpbin.org/json

###

### 测试 3: Body 数字断言
@name POST with Assertions
@assert status == 200
@assert body.json.number > 0
@assert body.json.number < 1000
POST https://httpbin.org/post
Content-Type: application/json

{"number": 42, "text": "test"}

###

### 测试 4: Body 字符串断言
@name String Assertion Test
@assert status == 200
@assert body.json.text == "hello"
POST https://httpbin.org/post
Content-Type: application/json

{"text": "hello"}

###

### 测试 5: Body null 检查
@name Null Check Test
@assert status == 200
@assert body.json.value != null
POST https://httpbin.org/post
Content-Type: application/json

{"value": "not null"}

###

### 测试 6: 嵌套路径断言
@name Nested Path Test
@assert status == 200
@assert body.json.user.name == "test"
@assert body.json.user.id > 0
POST https://httpbin.org/post
Content-Type: application/json

{"user": {"name": "test", "id": 123}}

###

### 测试 7: exists 断言
@name Exists Assertion Test
@assert status == 200
@assert body.json.token exists
@assert body.json.data exists
POST https://httpbin.org/post
Content-Type: application/json

{"token": "abc123", "data": {"key": "value"}}

###

### 测试 8: Header 断言
@name Header Assertion Test
@assert status == 200
@assert headers.server exists
@assert headers.content-type contains "application/json"
GET https://httpbin.org/headers

###

### 测试 9: 响应时间断言
@name Response Time Test
@assert status == 200
@assert response.time < 3000
@assert body.slideshow exists
GET https://httpbin.org/json

###

### 测试 10: 失败的断言（预期失败）
@name Failing Assertion Test
@assert status == 404
@assert body.message == "Not Found"
GET https://httpbin.org/status/200
